t-meta` before wiring\n`but-agentlog sync`.\n\n## Suggested Ref Shape\n\nAgentlog sync is key-scoped first. The serialized local ref and remote ref\nshould mirror that scope as directly as GitMeta allows:\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-11T16:53:42.000Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}